{"id":"981","name":"next-big-weekend-americana-music-festival","title":"Next Big Weekend: Americana Music Festival","author":"Morgan Levy","date":"2008-09-18T07:00:00-05:00","tags":["americana music festival","ben kweller","buddy miller","conference","country music hall of fame","grimey&apos;s","next big nashville","the groove"],"categories":["Music City"],"contentEncoded":"<div id=\"greet_block\"><noscript><div class=\"greet_block wpgb_cornered\"><div class=\"greet_text\"><div class=\"greet_image\"><a href=\"http://nashvillest.com/feed/rss/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"http://nashvillest.com/wp-content/plugins/wp-greet-box/images/rss_icon.png\" alt=\"WP Greet Box icon\"></a></div>Hello there! If you&apos;re new to Nashvillest, you might want to <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/nashvillest\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>subscribe to our RSS feed</strong></a> to make sure you don&apos;t miss anything! We&apos;re also on <a href=\"https://twitter.com/#!/nashvillest\" target=\"blank\"><strong>Twitter</strong></a> if you&apos;d like to join us there!<div style=\"clear:both\"></div><div class=\"greet_block_powered_by\">Powered by <a href=\"http://omninoggin.com/projects/wordpress-plugins/wp-greet-box-wordpress-plugin/\" title=\"WP Greet Box WordPress Plugin\" style=\"text-decoration:none;\">WP Greet Box</a> <a href=\"http://omninoggin.com/\" title=\"WordPress Plugin\" style=\"text-decoration:none;\">WordPress Plugin</a></div><div style=\"clear:both\"></div></div></div></noscript></div><p><img class=\"alignleft\" style=\"float: left;\" src=\"http://i33.tinypic.com/2l8ytzm.jpg\" alt=\"\"></p><p><a href=\"http://nashvillest.com/?s=next+big+nashville\" target=\"_blank\">Next Big Nashville</a> not really your thing? That&#x2019;s okay, because Nashville always has something for everyone. In this case, it&#x2019;s back to back weeks of incredible music festivals. While the <a href=\"http://www.americanamusic.org/site.php?content=conference\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.americanamusic.org&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">Americana Music Festival</a> is much smaller in scale than Next Big Nashville, it showcases some of the best talents in the nation, and includes a solid schedule of music industry events and educational <a href=\"http://www.americanamusic.org/site.php?content=conference_schedule\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.americanamusic.org&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">conference sessions</a>. We&#x2019;re still wiped out from our rendezvous with 2am (times 4 days) last week, but a bunch of the <a href=\"http://www.americanamusic.org/site.php?content=conference_schedule\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.americanamusic.org&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">showcases</a> have piqued our interest. With performances scheduled by artists from Buddy Miller to Ben Kweller (and everyone in between), there really is a show for everyone. Wristbands for all four nights (whoops, only three left) are only $35 and can be purchased at <a href=\"http://www.grimeys.com\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.grimeys.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">Grimey&#x2019;s</a>,&#xA0;<a href=\"http://www.countrymusichalloffame.com/site/\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.countrymusichalloffame.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">Country Music Hall of Fame</a>, or <a href=\"http://www.thegroovenashville.com/\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.thegroovenashville.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">The Groove</a>.</p><p>Related posts:<ol><li><a href=\"http://nashvillest.com/2008/07/21/this-weekend-music-city-brewers-festival/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent Link: This Weekend: Music City Brewer&#x2019;s Festival\">This Weekend: Music City Brewer&#x2019;s Festival</a></li><li><a href=\"http://nashvillest.com/2011/09/02/73rd-national-folk-festival-comes-to-nashville-this-weekend/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent Link: 73rd National Folk Festival Comes To Nashville This Weekend\">73rd National Folk Festival Comes To Nashville This Weekend</a></li><li><a href=\"http://nashvillest.com/2009/04/13/go-green-this-weekend-at-the-nashville-earth-day-festival/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent Link: Go Green This Weekend At The Nashville Earth Day Festival\">Go Green This Weekend At The Nashville Earth Day Festival</a></li></ol></p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<!--END .entry-content .article-->"}